Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.27,0:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This ice here's gonna get in the way.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then why don't we have two boats set off here,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and have this boat circle around?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.17,0:00:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the big day.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.41,0:00:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations sure go by fast \Nwhen the adults lend a hand.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they sure do.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.86,0:00:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a present.{gdi SYD ruined this line for me}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.91,0:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just leftover bread from the shop, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's plenty.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping your mom? Attaboy.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.69,0:00:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't he been a bit weird lately?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.51,0:00:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.81,0:00:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.96,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Akira, you're here, too?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.53,0:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, this'll be Akira-kun's first Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.05,0:00:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we haven't done one for a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.29,0:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take a closer look?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.47,0:00:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaka's.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.74,0:00:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.91,0:00:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This pendant...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.28,0:01:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is filled with Manaka-san's love.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaka's love...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.87,0:01:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!{kids, ruining everything since}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.69,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's moving so fast.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:21.09,0:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's not even a current.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.42,0:01:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:27.51,0:01:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dissolving!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.31,0:01:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.52,0:01:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,558)}I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.09,0:01:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love Hii-kun"...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.70,0:01:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.99,0:01:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You "knew it"?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.38,0:01:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I admired the sun.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.08,0:01:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the ocean, beyond the sky...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and ever so distant.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so bright.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It shone down on me.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It sparked a flame in me
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and made my heart race.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.86,0:02:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun's the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.61,0:02:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came out of the sea,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.90,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the sunlight-filled surface felt so fun, so exciting.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.09,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I realized I was able to admire the surface because the sea was there beside it.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.21,0:02:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the sea,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.72,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,my Ena dries up, and I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.39,0:02:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you love Hikari?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I know how Chii-chan feels.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.44,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She said not to tell anyone that she likes Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.65,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to tell anyone either.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.65,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's what you want?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.85,0:03:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say anything this whole time?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she asked me not to.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.57,0:03:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari tried so hard!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.90,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He believed Manaka-san's love was for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He really tried so hard to get it back.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari said it himself.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To get Mukaido's feelings back,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the person she loves has to work for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.39,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari's already done more than enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think love is like the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is like the sea?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just sweet and enjoyable.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.83,0:04:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to embrace the sadness, the pain, and everything else.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when new feelings are born.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.53,0:04:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So she...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.63,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}loved him back.
