Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.35,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari and Manaka-san loved each other.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.39,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Manaka-san gets back the ability to love after the Boatdrift Ceremony...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I'd like to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.03,0:04:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't understand what love is.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the waves won't go away.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the waves?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna-chan, when you put your hands there,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow, I feel a little better.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.71,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we stay like this for a while?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.87,0:05:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.09,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.75,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the outfit we'll be wearing as the Wooden Maiden's attendants.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd adjust the hems a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.93,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,About your feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to lie about anything anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither you nor Mukaido need to lie anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka loves Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am a terrible person.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.00,0:06:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hoped for a long time that Hikari would \Nalways love Manaka, and I still do to this day.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hoped that Manaka would always be protected by Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.89,0:06:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us loved each other so much that I didn't want anything to change.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.26,0:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted Hikari and Manaka to be in love with each other,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.69,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because that would keep our relationships unchanged from how they'd always been.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the case now.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no longer about keeping you four together.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in love with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.71,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're still hoping that they love each other.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You think too highly of yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.27,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just put two and two together.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think it over again.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you actually still thinking about it?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,About who I really love?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.70,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm pretty sure you're in love with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm trying to figure out how to get you to admit it.{smooth}{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna deny it this time?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.69,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold you?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.69,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.40,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't be the only one who finds happiness.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
