Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.71,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.99,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, where are you going this late at night?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.14,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd go check out the boat.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.10,0:09:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The boat?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about how tomorrow's the big day.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to make sure we didn't \Nmiss anything during the preparations.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.71,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Manaka-san's ability to love comes back.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the only thing at stake.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully we'll be able to do \Nsomething about the surface, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I'm worried about her ability to love.{tlc: acceptable?}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently that's the only thing you girls think about.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should worry more about the bigger pict—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You love Manaka-san, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking abou—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You love her, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it again!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.81,0:09:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it again.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that you love Manaka-san again.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.10,0:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Have you lost it?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In return for all the things I've done for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you get off?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.87,0:10:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.07,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.12,0:10:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.94,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.67,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, would you give it a res—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.45,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.67,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It hurts...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The love that I feel for Hikari... hurts.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need it to hurt worse and worse
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.57,0:10:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to push my feelings for Hikari to a breaking point
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I can feel like throwing them away.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, will I...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.26,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will I be able to give up on Hikari?{not the best place to take a nap}{its abandoned, it runs straight into the ocean}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.99,Maschinenzimmer.412,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&H551B12&\fscx57\fscy57\pos(534,208)}Nishiura
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats, old man Kihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:29.00,Maschinenzimmer.412,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&HD37371&\pos(15,116)\fscx90\fscy90}Nishiura
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.28,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear you're finally allowed to go out.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to check the program.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, look up a little.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,First we need to get the spirit fire from {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.15,0:11:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing this Boatdrift Ceremony without any help from the sea,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.78,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's different from usual \Nand a bit more complicated.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.35,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the letter.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Kancho{Up your butt}!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose love...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,must be gratitude.{this is her theorizing what love may be, not what love is. her contact with the word 'love' is based on akiras childish letter, so she theorizes that being grateful is loving him back. this is weird on purpose because shes obviously not supposed to actually understand love}{"i suppose love... must be gratitude"}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.27,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that outfit looks so much better on adults than junior high school kids.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.42,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.65,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I played telephone with Tsumugu?{do telephones even exist in this world}{they do, you can sometimes see landline telephones}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For a lot of things.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.43,0:12:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki, you're not thinking of anything weird, are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.18,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Like planning to take the \NWooden Maiden's place this time.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us were always together.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I was left on the surface by myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko} has arrived!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}.{nice ride}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you confine me to such a small space?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like a big shot.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.55,0:13:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am a big shot. What did you expect?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Wooden Maiden.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.18,0:14:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks nothing like the real thing, as usual.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.22,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So the original maiden was a lot prettier?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a real shrimp of a girl, \Ncovered in freckles,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and frail to boot.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they called it a sacrifice,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.18,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it was a convenient way for the surface dwellers to get rid of people they didn't need.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You... loved the original maiden, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.87,0:14:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you fell off the sea god, you were the same person—
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or rather, the same god, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.31,0:14:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you really okay with letting the maiden return to the surface like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.90,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was kinda around the \Nsea god's shoulder-blade area.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.57,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had been a scale on his right hand, \NI could have touched her hair.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.50,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had been on his left hand, \NI could have held her.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.95,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, as soon as I fell off, \Nthe sea god and I became separate entities.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that happened, \NI became but a mere scale.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A scale from his shoulder blade, at that.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I speak of the maiden?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to begin!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So show me, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.31,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me what you can change
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you cannot.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Hikari and the others.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea God...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.25,0:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you respond \Nto the efforts of your children?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.97,0:17:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Under your divine benevolence,{this prayer or whatever it is also appears in ep 05. consistency for batch would be good}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.22,0:17:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we, the people of Shioshishio,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,have always respected, honored and served
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.42,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,our father, our god, the mighty sea god,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.78,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the years since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.86,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,O Sea God, most exalted one, protect us, your children.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless us, and grant us prosperity.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A storm's coming.{oh boy}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the sea was so calm!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san!{they never learn, do they}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to save her!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka doesn't have Ena!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.38,0:18:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hold onto the boat!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get thrown off!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.92,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.89,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.85,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The seawater is suffocating me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so rough.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It hurts.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.64,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sea had always protected me, but now...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea is responding to Miuna's feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.11,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukaido loves Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and so does Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukaido's feelings and \NMiuna's feelings are very similar.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.26,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the feelings of Mukaido's \Nthat dissolved into the sea are shining.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.35,0:19:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can sense them.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.64,0:20:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can sense your feelings, Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm with you like this, Miuna-chan,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so at ease.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.63,0:20:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because my Ena is shouting that it loves Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.49,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.18,0:20:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.95,0:20:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shouting that it loves the sea \Nand everyone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.31,0:20:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This presence...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the Wooden Maidens' graveyard?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.02,0:21:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea God, you bastard!{more like okada, you bastard}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.11,0:21:38.88,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.52,0:21:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:46.35,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:48.03,0:21:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Hii-kun. I love Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Hii-kun.{xn}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.46,0:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:57.54,0:21:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:00.28,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.00,0:22:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love... you...{rip}
